item.description:
Steps to follow
- Login to Admin panel
- Turn off Maintenance
- Login
- Create car by VIN
- Select inspections  Pre- inspection
- Start inspections  Pre- inspection
- Finish inspection  Pre- inspection
- Recive list of inspections
- Select inspections  Post- inspection
- Start inspections  Post- inspection
- Finish inspection  Post- inspection
- Recive list of inspections and check duplicate
- Recive list of inspections and save ID of 10 issues
